list_page_teaser: Scott & Cathy have been going together for many years.  Click to learn more!
description_html:
Scott and Cathy have been together for many years, and seem to get along well with everyone. What's their secret?

Hopefully they will share some of their tips for how they make their relationship last. Check back soon for updates!
story_html:
I met Scott and Cathy at the Goth clubs in Denver, Colorado. These images are something for them to look at before I ask them to share their story.

I will share more information as it becomes available. To learn when I update the site, follow us on social media or join the email list!

image_list.title: Scott
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: The Green and Blue in Scott's spiritual portrait say he is passionate and down-to-earth.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Green in this portrait represents Scott's dominant trait, his objectivity - which is very slight.  In Extraverts, the dominant trait is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long vertical line to represent this, because it is the side of their personality that is most evident.
image_list.explain_aux: The Blue in this portrait represents Scott's auxiliary trait, his idealism - which is very slight.  In Extraverts, the auxiliary trait is directed inwardly and is less evident than the dominant trait.
image_list.story_html:
Scott lives in Denver, Colorado.

I will share more information as it becomes available.

image_list.title: Cathy
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: The Red and Yellow in Cathy's spiritual portrait say he is rational and idealistic.  Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Yellow in this portrait represents Cathy's dominant trait, her realism.  In Introverts, the dominant trait is directed inwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long horizontal line to represent this.
image_list.explain_aux: The Red in this portrait represents Cathy's auxiliary trait, her compassion.  In Introverts, the auxiliary trait is directed outwardly and is more evident than the dominant trait.
image_list.story_html:
Cathy lives in Denver, Colorado.

I will share more information as it becomes available.
